    <item>
      <title>中国股市因假期回升而追涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-05/chinese-stocks-yuan-primed-for-gains-on-return-from-holidays</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国股市和在岸人民币在假期结束后上涨，北京的支持性政策立场和消费持续复苏的迹象提振了市场情绪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-05/chinese-stocks-yuan-primed-for-gains-on-return-from-holidays</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 05 May 2024 23:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
